>>47558627
I like lewds in 2nd or limited 3rd. For SFW it's just about style.

1st lives and dies by how good your protagonist is. 2nd is harder to use for SFW because it gives you a kind of "dungeon master" narrator that makes self insertion easy but characterisation harder. Limited 3rd is generally what I like best. Although it doesn't have to be very strictly limited, since you usually end up somewhere between purely limited and purely omniscient with 3rd.
